  "text": "Two adjunctive techniques have also been reported: one aimed at enhancing fusion across the joint using electromagnetic field alongside various methods of arthrodesis performed [CITATION_1] and the other employed computer assisted navigation to improve the accuracy of the cuts and alignment after which an Ilizarov EF was applied [CITATION_2] .",
